  "texts": [
    "This is more important in the case of the user-centric explainable recommendation system because lay users are unlikely to comprehend algorithmic explanations.",
    "Therefore, apart from collecting usage patterns and user interactions, it will also be beneficial if recommendation platforms can collect users' feedback explicitly to deliver them a proper explanation.",
    "The explicit feedback mechanism will help the platform developers develop and incorporate end user-centric explanation mechanisms.",
    "This requirement can vary from user to user.",
    "According to the explanation provided by Miller (2019), cognitive biases are present when a user selects and evaluates an explanation (Miller, 2019)."
  ],
